From Little Seeds Grow Mighty Trees 🌴🌳

At ArthMod, we believe in maximum efficiency and sustainability. With every purchase, we give you a handmade plantme card. These cards are made up of seed paper which can be turned into a beautiful plant after usage.

All it requires is a pot, some water, a little sunshine and care. This indeed is a complimentary gift for you and for mother अर्थ ✨🍀
